      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "-> Map performs operations on each element.\n\nconst nums = [1,2,3,4];\n\nconst result = nums.map(num=>num*2);\n\nconsole.log(result);\n\n-> map function will return a new array. not change original array.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "-> Map performs operations on each element.\n\nconst nums = [1,2,3,4];\n\nconst result = nums.map(num=>num*2);\n\nconsole.log(result);\n\n-> map function will return a new array. not change original array.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
